{
  "stem": "25639.10",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that's the only thing I will accept.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, Youth Aliyah was after me to come on the next boat and the next boat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were periodically boats-- I'm not so sure that I can call them ships-- that were not given up to par that were smuggled into Israel at the time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time it was called Palestine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as you know, the British was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the White Paper, well, prevented us from entering that country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I was going to go on a ship, if I don't hear from anyone, I was going to go on a ship.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for some reason, I can't remember why, I just remember telling the gentleman who came over to the house that the next one, the next one will be at [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If I don't hear by then, I'm going to go with the next ship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the ship that I turned down ended up in Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was big banner headlines that the British has captured this ship and all the passengers-- almost all of them former concentration camp inmates-- landed in Cyprus behind barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think-- I don't know what the name of the ship was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were others, too, that landed in Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, the Swedish Red Cross took care of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, actually not-- actually they had to work with the organization, the Youth Aliyah, that worked with me on that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still have the registration papers, blank.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did not fill them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just couldn't get myself to fill it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because until I hear from home that somebody was alive, I couldn't accept the fact that nobody survived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, from Sweden.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
